// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0204 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 3522831f-5787-532e-adb9-ec4d2463f471

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:2*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*")
